<li id="cite_note-13"><b><a href="#cite_ref-13" title="">^</a></b> Contingency, Irony, and Solidarity. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 1989. ISBN, p 44</li>
<li id="cite_note-14"><b><a href="#cite_ref-14" title="">^</a></b> Contingency, Irony, and Solidarity. Cambridge: Cambridge University Press, 1989. ISBN, p 48</li>
</ol>
</div>


